Title: Series: Life of Christ
Description: Flight into Egypt; the Virgin holds the Christ child and rides on a donkey to left led by St Joseph who has a staff over his shoulder; circular design surrounded by a rectangular ornamental framework Engraving with faded hand-colour
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (87) (XIII, p.121-)
